cateLongName: Dmx Controller of dj lighting equipment
productName: 192CH DMX console DC-001
productInfo:
512CH DMX console DC-007

1.DMX512/1990 standard,512 DMX control channels.
2. 2 output with optical isolated,withstand 2000Vrms.Independent slot structure,which is easy to change.
3.Up to 32 scanners may be connected with a maximum of 16 channels each.
4.A large backlight LCD to display operation parameters.
5.16 sliders for channel,1 slider for speed control.
6.1600 chase steps,48 chases,up to 100 steps each.Each step contains its speed and cross time,can be set respectively.Trigger mode selectable:Music synchronously and manual speed.
7.Cooperating with the chase speed slider,the time of the program step can be changed from 0.03s to 180s.
8.48 scanner scenes can be used directly.
9.4 chases,48 scenes operated at the same time.At most 32 scanners can be selected simultaneously.
10.The X/Y channels of different scanners can be controlled by modulation wheel.
11.16 bit control for absolutely precise movement.
12.15 environment programs to output the combination,which are composed of different scenes,chases and manual output quickly.
13.The music trigger source can be selected between audio line input or inside microphone.
14.Easy to edit and handle.
15.The data auto-saves.
16.High performance switching power supply,with extremely low power harmonious distortion and wide range of voltage,suit for the requirement of different country

1.DMX512/1990 standard,512 DMX control channels.

12.15 environment programs to output the combination,which are composed of different scenes,chases and manual output quickly.

16.High performance switching power supply,with extremely low power harmonious distortion and wide range of voltage,suit for the requirement of different country
